Description: Egypt or Israel [?], small group of adult males sitting in row in front of stone building. Two adult females and a child sitting at other side of gateway. Males wearing gowns, turbans. Females wearing cloths covering heads. Medium: Gelatin silver print.
Producer name: Photographed by: John Frederick Clifford Hunt
Curator's comments: Circumstances: The Imperial War Museum holds photographs from the same collection with a more military content - see [HUN-] PIC DOC 66.
